Imprisoner/Predator/Choran:


A few lasers knocked Imprisoner to his chest, not that badly damaged, but he 
didn't want to take the chance.  Transforming to his vehicle mode, similar to 
a train, only bigger.  Smashing through the trees quickly, his companions 
hopped on, a missile striking the back of his heavily armored mode, shaking 
him lightly.  Smashing through trees at 50 MPH and climbing, Imprisoner 
chuckled madly.
